Task:Create a login page that connects to your portfolio
1. Make a login page with your preferred design.
2. It will be composed of email, password,agree checkbox and then 
submit btn.
3.Each input needs to have a validations as follows:
    a.email-validate if inputted is email.
    b.password-validate if correct.
    c.agree-validate if this was clicked before proceeding.
    d.submit-will be disabled while the form input is still not correct or 
        not the input/s are empty.
    e.inputs-need have a red color when submitted empty or not correct.
    f.labels-will change the color depends if wrong or correct the input